      "message": "Done in PS33/PS36. The mlx5 TX helpers now take a compile-time is_tso parameter and rdma_device_output_tx_try() selects the TSO/non-TSO clone once from RDMA_DEVICE_F_TSO, so the non-TSO path compiles out the GSO checks and TSO calls.",
